drop external table externalaggtempextremes
drop table aggtempextremes
CREATE EXTERNAL TABLE ExternalAggTempExtremes (
	date VARCHAR(100),
    max_temp_F FLOAT,
    min_temp_F FLOAT
)
WITH (
    LOCATION = 'gold/agg_temp_extremes/part-00000-c514cc1b-f4c9-4911-a082-8d43e438cce1-c000.snappy.parquet',
    DATA_SOURCE = MyDataSource,
    FILE_FORMAT = ParquetFileFormat
);

CREATE TABLE AggTempExtremes (
	date VARCHAR(100),
    max_temp_F FLOAT,
    min_temp_F FLOAT
);
INSERT INTO AggTempExtremes (
    date,
    max_temp_F,
    min_temp_F
)
SELECT DISTINCT
    date,
    max_temp_F,
    min_temp_F
FROM ExternalAggTempExtremes;
GO
